This directory contains a custom dataset containing high-quality writing about economics.
There is a folder called data not present in the git repository because of its size. This folder contains the raw text data that composes the dataset
Dataset sources (will be updated as more data is found):
- themoneyillusion.com: Scott Sumner's blog. Scott is a macroeconomist focused on monetary matters. 
- voxeu: CEPR columns about economic research

